The brushes are from @nycake, @sweetsticksau, and Wilton

I made two other cookies - one for each of my daughters - which I'll be sharing soon 😄

Swipe to see the tracing board in action. 

You can watch the full tutorial and read more about this gadget on my blog. Clickable link in my bio
